<p>
<lb n="1"/>Asti calamarttigaṁḍaḥ paranṛpajīvāpaharaṇakarayamadaṇḍaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sadguṇaratnakaraṇḍaḥ kavi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>janaśiṣṭēṣṭavanajavanamārttaṁḍaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yēna kṣitīśvaravarēṇa maṇīṣivārddhi(ḥ)
<lb n="3" break="no"/>puṇyāni ratnakalitātulajīvanāni <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śasvadvivriddhimahitāni ciraṁttanāni dhattēssamujvala
<lb n="4" break="no"/>yeśō lalitōttamāni <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> yasya kṣitīśvaravarasya bhujāsidhārā saṁpūjitā vijayakanya
<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>ka</unclear>yā vibhāti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nirbhbhinnavairigajamastakapīṭhajātamuktākṣatāṁccitakarāṁbujayā (sa)raṇāgrē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation">.</g>
